{"id":1730491,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-13T13:44:33.786Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1730491,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"3 Nota Cinta","overview":"# The Story of Alisa  Alisa (Sharifah Rose) is frequently a victim of her mother Sofea's (Zila Bakarin) anger ever since her father Razak (Khairil Anwar Aman) abandoned them without a word several years ago. Sofea was forced to seek a dissolution of marriage, resulting in a third talak (divorce). Alisa's family was shattered and Sofea's demeanor changed drastically. Sofea became quick-tempered and began controlling the lives of her unmarried children. Sofea's relationship with her parents, Bahar and Aminah, also became strained as Sofea blamed them as the main reason Razak abandoned her. Bahar began showing signs of forgetfulness and sometimes could not take care of himself. After being diagnosed with Alzheimer's disease, love notes written by him in Jawi script became the most precious memories for Aminah. Alisa admires her grandfather and grandmother's unwavering love that remained steadfast despite being tested by various incidents.","popularity":0.0143,"poster_path":"/tTTcBS6tZgaYxxdOOsdr1HGehli.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":85597,"logo_path":null,"name":"Orangetree Production Sdn Bhd","origin_country":""}],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2022-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"3 Nota Cinta","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":1344453,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Ashraf Muslim","original_name":"Ashraf Muslim","popularity":0.3963,"profile_path":"/pbcblRckfciCK3g0VUiTHNKF4Yk.jpg","cast_id":2,"character":"","credit_id":"6a539d1a81aa637cb2f5dbe8","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":